    },
    {
      "beat_id": "B04",
      "act": "THE PROBLEM",
      "t_start": 27,
      "estimated_duration_s": 9,
      "narration_text": "The second-order correction is a sum over all other energy levels. Each term has a matrix element in the numerator and an energy difference in the denominator.",
      "shot": {
        "type": "GRAPHIC",
        "source": "own",
        "motion": "drawon"
      },
      "audio_file": "../vox-second-order-negative/mp3/beat-B04.mp3",
      "actual_duration_s": 8.67,
      "locked": true,
      "source_clip": "../vox-second-order-negative/clips/B04.mp4",
      "source_audio": "../vox-second-order-negative/mp3/beat-B04.mp3"
    },
    {
      "beat_id": "B05",
      "act": "THE PROBLEM",
      "t_start": 36,
      "estimated_duration_s": 9,
      "narration_text": "The numerator is a squared magnitude — a number times its own conjugate. It is never negative. That part alone cannot determine the sign.",
      "shot": {
        "type": "GRAPHIC",
        "source": "own",
        "motion": "drawon"
      },
      "audio_file": "../vox-second-order-negative/mp3/beat-B05.mp3",
      "actual_duration_s": 8.86,
      "locked": true,
      "source_clip": "../vox-second-order-negative/clips/B05.mp4",
      "source_audio": "../vox-second-order-negative/mp3/beat-B05.mp3"
    },
    {
      "beat_id": "B06",
      "act": "THE PROBLEM",
      "t_start": 45,
      "estimated_duration_s": 10,
      "narration_text": "So the sign must come from the denominator: the ground-state energy minus the energy of each excited level. That difference is always negative — every excited level sits above the ground state.",
      "shot": {
        "type": "STILL",
        "source": "ai",
        "motion": "kenburns",
        "remotion": {
          "pattern": "SlateCard",
          "provenance": "proven-core/SlateCard",
          "version": "1",
          "props": {
            "headline": "So the sign must come from the denominator: the ground-state energy…",
            "eyebrow": "THE PROBLEM",
            "topic": "QUANTUM MECHANICS"
          },
          "rendered": {
            "out": "media/B06.mp4",
            "at": ""
          }
        }
      },
      "audio_file": "../vox-second-order-negative/mp3/beat-B06.mp3",
      "actual_duration_s": 12.36,
      "locked": true,
      "source_clip": "../vox-second-order-negative/clips/B06.mp4",
