      "act": "THE IMPLICATION",
      "t_start": 96,
      "estimated_duration_s": 10,
      "narration_text": "This is not just a curiosity. It is why the variational principle works: any trial state gives an energy above the ground state, and the second-order correction approaches it from above.",
